'''瑞貝卡‧「貝卡」‧梅莉絲‧托賓''' ([[英語|英語]]：'''Rebecca "Becca" Melise Tobin'''；1986年1月18日－) <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20130105021107/http://blogs.ajc.com/the-buzz/2013/01/02/interview-cobb-native-becca-tobin-shines-in-glee-role/?icid=buzzlink "Interview: Cobb native Becca Tobin shines in "Glee" role"]. AJC.com. January 2, 2013. Archived from [http://blogs.ajc.com/the-buzz/2013/01/02/interview-cobb-native-becca-tobin-shines-in-glee-role/?icid=buzzlink the original] on January 5, 2013.</ref>，又簡稱為「貝卡·托賓」，為[[美國|美國]]女演員、[[歌手|歌手]]以及[[舞者|舞者]]，她的知名作品包括電視節目的《[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]》。
==早期生活==
貝卡出生於美國喬治亞州瑪麗埃塔城市，貝卡是家裡兩個女兒的小妹，父母都是律師，她曾經在七年級以及八年級時加入啦啦隊，但之後認為不適合她並轉而學習舞蹈。她在高一時從戲劇學校轉到公立學校，之後開始被霸凌，有些人稱呼她為「劇院怪胎」以及「阿宅」，並且說她永遠不會成名或者變成明星，其中一位女生威脅說要揍她，貝卡也收過惡意的簡訊並且連唯一的朋友都開始疏遠她。由於霸凌，貝卡拒絕參加一些學校活動，例如賽前集會，她也並未參加畢業典禮。<ref>[http://www.wetpaint.com/glee/articles/becca-tobin-opens-up-about-being-bullied-in-high-school-and-reveals-whats-next-for-kitty-on-glee-season-4-exclusive "Becca Tobin Opens Up About Being Bullied in High School – and Reveals What's Next for Kitty on Glee Season 4! Exclusive"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wetpaint.com/glee/articles/becca-tobin-opens-up-about-being-bullied-in-high-school-and-reveals-whats-next-for-kitty-on-glee-season-4-exclusive |date=20190726183413 }}. Wetpaint.com. November 2012.</ref>2004年，她從惠勒高中畢業。她就讀過美國音樂及戲劇學院。

==職業生涯==
貝卡的首部作品為四歲時在學校表演的耶誕樹<ref>[http://www.celebuzz.com/2012-12-26/glees-becca-tobin-shares-christmas-flashback-her-hilarious-and-awkward-first-role-exclusive-photo/ "Glee's Becca Tobin Shares Christmas Flashback: Her 'Hilarious' and 'Awkward' First Role"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.celebuzz.com/2012-12-26/glees-becca-tobin-shares-christmas-flashback-her-hilarious-and-awkward-first-role-exclusive-photo/ |date=20191014164759 }}. Celebuzz.com. Retrieved December 26, 2012.</ref>，於18歲時，貝卡搬到紐約開始工作。她在百老匯擔任過替身，之後也在其他小型劇院擔任過替身工作。
貝卡在福斯電視台的影集《[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]》中飾演 Kitty Wilde 。<ref>[http://www.playbill.com/news/article/becca-tobin-and-melissa-benoist-join-foxs-glee-ryan-murphy-dishes-on-upcomi-196306 Gioia, Michael (August 2, 2012). "Becca Tobin and Melissa Benoist Join Fox's "Glee"; Ryan Murphy Dishes on Upcoming Season Via Twitter"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/becca-tobin-and-melissa-benoist-join-foxs-glee-ryan-murphy-dishes-on-upcomi-196306 |date=20190729003942 }}. Playbill.</ref>她第一次現身在第四季第一集《The New Rachel》，之後以常設角色身分出現在該季，具報導指出她會在第五季成為主要角色。<ref>Ausiello, Michael (June 28, 2013). [http://www.tvline.com/2013/06/28/glee-season-5-cast-heather-morris-mark-salling-not-returning/ "UPDATED Glee Exclusive: 4 Original Cast Members are Returning as Series Regulars for Season 5; Plus – Who's Getting Promoted?"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tvline.com/2013/06/28/glee-season-5-cast-heather-morris-mark-salling-not-returning/ |date=20190227205142 }}. TVLine. Retrieved July 1, 2013.</ref>

==私人生活==
貝卡曾與一名夜店老闆 Matt Bendik 交往，直到對方在2014年7月10日過世，其原因是因喝海洛因過量而致死。<ref>Chiu, Melody (July 11, 2014). [http://people.com/article/glee-star-becca-tobin-boyfirned-matt-bendik-found-dead-philadelphia-hotel-room "Glee Star Becca Tobin's Boyfriend Found Dead, Cause of Death Unknown"] {{Wayback|url=http://people.com/article/glee-star-becca-tobin-boyfirned-matt-bendik-found-dead-philadelphia-hotel-room |date=20140715022347 }}. People. Retrieved July 29, 2014.</ref>不過後來，在2016年5月，貝卡在與企業家 Zach Martin 交往<ref>Johnson, Zach (May 17, 2016). [http://www.eonline.com/news/765498/glee-s-becca-tobin-is-engaged-to-zach-martin "Glee's Becca Tobin Is Engaged to Zach Martin"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/765498/glee-s-becca-tobin-is-engaged-to-zach-martin |date=20160518225850 }}. E! News. Retrieved May 17, 2016.</ref>，兩人並在2016年12月3日正式結婚。<ref>Sands, Nicole (December 3, 2016). [http://people.com/tv/lea-michele-reunion-photo-becca-tobin-zach-martins-wedding/ "It's a Glee-union! Lea Michele Shares Photo with Cast at Becca Tobin's Wedding"] {{Wayback|url=http://people.com/tv/lea-michele-reunion-photo-becca-tobin-zach-martins-wedding/ |date=20191218130124 }}. People.</ref><ref>Cuccinelli, Jamie (December 4, 2016). [http://www.brides.com/story/becca-tobin-wedding-photos "Glee's Becca Tobin is Married! See Her Exclusive Wedding Photos"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.brides.com/story/becca-tobin-wedding-photos |date=20191204092946 }}. Brides.</ref>
